MIP 2
"multum in parvo"
(much in little)

----------

plugin wrappers, abstractions, simplifications, helpers, ..
in progress, prototype, proof of concept, pre-, ..

* os: linux (windows considered)
* gui: xcb (cairo incoming)
* plugin: clap (exe, vst2, vst3, maybe lv2 coming)
* host: clap (other formats considered)

* headers-only
* un-modern, un-cool c++
* no (minimal) dependencies
* ...

* make it work
* make it right
* make it fast, small, stable, bugfree, pretty, etc..

----------

see also:
(most of this is already ported over to MIP2, or will be soon)

mip:              https://github.com/skei/MIP
claphost:         https://github.com/skei/MIP/tree/master/apps
simple mpe synth: https://github.com/skei/MIP/tree/master/plugins/templates
kode3:            https://github.com/skei/kode3
